feature-based-structure: Organize code by feature/domain, not by artifact type.
single-responsibility: One component, service, hook, or util per file.
filename-matches-export: Name files after their default export (e.g. UserService.ts).
subfolder-on-growth: Create subfolders when a features codebase grows.
respect-folder-structure: Make sure to place thing where they belong (e.g. type and shape related stuff in the types directory).